## Purpose

Aartiq is a cross-platform browser with native AI orchestration capabilities. It allows users to control browser automation through natural language commands, execute shell commands safely, schedule background tasks, and sync across devices with end-to-end encryption.

## Core Capabilities

1. AI-powered browser automation via natural language
2. Local LLM support through Ollama integration
3. Background task scheduling that runs when browser is closed
4. End-to-end encrypted cross-device synchronization
5. Native plugin system for extensibility
6. OCR-based screen recognition and element clicking
7. PDF generation through AI commands
8. Shell command execution with permission levels

## Technical Stack

- Desktop: Electron with native Node.js modules
- Frontend: Next.js 14, React 18, TypeScript
- Mobile: Flutter
- AI Providers: Google Gemini, OpenAI GPT, Anthropic Claude, Ollama

